#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_training.md:1
msgid "Becoming a Trainer"
msgstr "Convertirse en un Trainer"

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_training.md:2
msgid ""
"The Trainers group periodically accepts new members via application. New "
"Trainers undergo an eight-week training program outlined below and agree to "
"the Trainer Agreement."
msgstr ""
"El grupo de Trainers acepta periódicamente nuevos miembros a través de las "
"aplicaciones. Los nuevos Trainers se someten a un programa de training de "
"ocho semanas que se describe a continuación y aceptan el Acuerdo de "
"Trainers."

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_training.md:4
msgid "Trainers Training Program"
msgstr "Programa Trainers Training"

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_training.md:6
msgid ""
"This outline represents the time commitment required for being an instructor"
" Trainer with the Carpentries. Please read through and check to see that you"
" are able to commit to the responsibilities outlined below."
msgstr ""
"Este bosquejo representa el compromiso de tiempo requerido para ser "
"instructores de Trainer con las Carpentries. Leer y verificar la posibilidad"
" de comprometerse con las responsabilidades que se detallan a continuación."

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_training.md:8
msgid ""
"Instructor Trainers agree to abide by the Code of Conduct in all "
"communications and interactions with The Carpentries community."
msgstr ""
"Los instructores de Trainers acuerdan cumplir con el Código de conducta en "
"todas las comunicaciones e interacciones con la comunidad de The "
"Carpentries."

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_training.md:10
msgid ""
"Read How Learning Works by Susan Ambrose and discuss in book club format "
"with Trainers-in-training. Preliminary reading schedule."
msgstr ""
"Leer cómo funciona el aprendizaje de Susan Ambrose y discutir en formato de "
"club de lectura con Trainers en formación. Calendario de lectura preliminar."

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_training.md:11
msgid ""
"Time commitment: 1 hour per week for 8 weeks meetings; can miss one meeting;"
" ~10 hours reading"
msgstr ""
"Compromiso de tiempo: 1 hora por semana para meetings de 8 semanas; puede "
"faltar a una meeting; ~10 horas de lectura"

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_training.md:12
msgid "Join Trainer meetings"
msgstr "Unirse a las meetings de Trainers"

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_training.md:13
msgid "Time commitment: 1 hour per month; can miss one meeting"
msgstr "Compromiso de tiempo: 1 hora por mes; puede faltar a una meeting"

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_training.md:14
msgid "Shadow a teaching demonstration session"
msgstr "Presenciar una sesión de demostración de enseñanza como shadow"

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_training.md:15
msgid "Time commitment: 1 hour one time"
msgstr "Compromiso de tiempo: 1 hora una vez."

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_training.md:16
msgid "Shadow at least half a day of an online instructor training event"
msgstr ""
"Presenciar al menos medio día de un evento de capacitación de instructores "
"en línea como shadow"

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_training.md:17
msgid "Time commitment: 4 hours one time"
msgstr "Compromiso de tiempo: 4 horas una vez"

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_training.md:18
msgid ""
"Teach once either online or in person with experienced Trainer (after "
"finishing book club)"
msgstr ""
"Enseñe una vez en línea o en persona con un Trainer experimentado (después "
"de terminar el club de lectura)"

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_training.md:19
msgid "Time commitment: 2 days one time plus prep"
msgstr "Compromiso de tiempo: 2 días una vez más preparación"

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_training.md:20
msgid "Agree to the Trainer Agreement."
msgstr "Aceptar el trainer agreement"

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_training.md:22
msgid ""
"Total time commitment for continuing Trainers: 4 days per year + 2.5 hrs per"
" month"
msgstr ""
"Compromiso de tiempo total para Trainers continuos: 4 días por año + 2.5 "
"horas por mes"

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_training.md:25
msgid ""
"Total time commitment for new Trainers: 3 days + ~30 hours over 3 month "
"period, including reading and prep time"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_training.md:28
msgid "Trainers Training Reading Schedule"
msgstr "calendario de lectura  de Trainers Training "

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_training.md:30
msgid ""
"For the most recent Trainer Training schedule and discussion questions, see "
"the Trainer Training Curriculum"
msgstr ""

